    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "ingredient_1_full_description",
      "label": "Full description (for popup)",
      "default": "<p>Shea Butter is a natural fat extracted from the nut of the African shea tree. It soothes irritated skin and creates a moisture-locking barrier that blocks bacteria. Rich in vitamins A, E, and F, it offers anti-inflammatory and healing properties that help maintain skin health.</p>"
    },
    {
