      "label": "Short description",
      "default": "Calms inflammation and supports skin healing, helping keep pores clean."
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "ingredient_2_full_description",
      "label": "Full description (for popup)",
      "default": "<p>Aloe Vera is a succulent plant species with gel-filled leaves that have been used for centuries for their healing properties. It calms inflammation and supports skin healing, helping keep pores clean. The gel contains vitamins, minerals, amino acids, and antioxidants that promote healthy skin.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Ingredient 3"
