    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ingredient_3_description",
      "label": "Short description",
      "default": "Draws out dirt, sweat, and toxins that feed odor-causing bacteria."
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "ingredient_3_full_description",
      "label": "Full description (for popup)",
      "default": "<p>Activated Charcoal is a fine black powder made from carbon-rich materials like wood, coconut shells, or peat that has been processed to have small, low-volume pores. It draws out dirt, sweat, and toxins that feed odor-causing bacteria, making it an excellent detoxifying agent for skin care products.</p>"
    },
    {
