      "label": "Title",
      "default": "Coconut Oil"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ingredient_4_description",
      "label": "Short description",
      "default": "Kills odor-causing bacteria on the skin with its antimicrobial properties."
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "ingredient_4_full_description",
      "label": "Full description (for popup)",
      "default": "<p>Coconut Oil is extracted from the meat of mature coconuts and is rich in medium-chain fatty acids. It kills odor-causing bacteria on the skin with its antimicrobial properties. The oil is also deeply moisturizing and helps strengthen the skin's natural barrier function.</p>"
    },
    {
