      "id": "ingredient_5_description",
      "label": "Short description",
      "default": "Provides a fresh citrus scent while naturally neutralizing bacteria."
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "ingredient_5_full_description",
      "label": "Full description (for popup)",
      "default": "<p>Bergamot Fruit Oil is cold-pressed from the rinds of bergamot oranges. It provides a fresh citrus scent while naturally neutralizing bacteria. The oil contains natural antiseptic properties and helps balance skin oils while providing a refreshing, uplifting aroma.</p>"
