      "default": "<p>Cedarwood Oil is derived from the wood of cedar trees. It adds a clean, masculine aroma and balances oil production. The oil has natural astringent properties that help tighten pores and reduce excess oil, making it particularly beneficial for men's skin care products.</p>"
